      Parameters:
      mode - mode of the game (easy or expert).
      preset - preset of the game (two, three or four players).
      state - state of the game (uninitialized, started, ended).
      phase - phase of the round in the game (planning or the action phases).
      currentPlayer - the current player.
      islandsView - view of the Islands.
      playersView - view of the Players.
      motherNatureIndex - index of the islands on which mother nature is on.
      cloudViews - the list of CloudView.

    • GameView

      constructor of the GameView for an expert game (sets also the attributes for the CharacterCard)
      Parameters:
      mode - mode of the game (easy or expert).
      preset - preset of the game (two, three or four players).
      state - state of the game (uninitialized, started, ended).
      phase - phase of the round in the game (planning or the action phases).
      currentPlayer - the current player.
      islandsView - view of the Islands.
      playersView - view of the Players.
      motherNatureIndex - index of the islands on which mother nature is on.
      reserve - reserve of coins.
      characterCardView - view of the character cards.
      playerCoins - coins of each player.
      cloudViews - the list of CloudView.
